L. E. HEIZER v. Pat KEATHLY, d/b/a Funeral Car Exchange. Lavone ENLOW v. Pat KEATHLY, d/b/a Funeral Car Exchange. Nos. 5804, 5805. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Aug. 7, 1958. Poe, Murdock & Langford, Tulsa, Okl., for appellants. Duvall & Head, Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeals dismissed on motion of appellants.
